Weeks 1–2 — Kombinatorik (Steps 1–4)
Topics: Additions- & multiplikationsprincipen, permutationer, kombinationer, binomialsatsen.
Materials: Chapter 1 (pages 5–55)
Plan:
Step 1: Read §1.1–1.2 — Additions- & multiplikationsprincipen, Permutationer. Do (-) and (A) exercises 1–15.
Step 2: §1.3 — Kombinationer. Practice exercises 20–29.
Step 3: §1.4–1.5 — Binomialsatsen, Kombinationer med upprepningar. Exercises 30–46.
